"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**主持人：橙子**\\n\\n**大家好，我是橙子，今天我们很荣幸邀请到了LOCGame的CEO MikhailMironov做客币橙社区。**\\n\\n **Welcome Mikhail Mironov**\\n\\n **下面正式进入今天的AMA环节，大家也可以提前准备问题，等AAM结束之后可以向嘉宾提问哈；**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/CRjXxZAuT0Uqu6Cvgkx-p.jpg?height=690&width=1280)\\n\\n**1.Self-Introduction (Introduce yourself & provide brief background):**\\n\\n**首先请向自我介绍一下：**\\n\\n嘉宾：Mik Mironov\\n\\nI am Mik Mironov, founder of LegendsOfCrypto (LOCGame) and RBL Labs (a part of Crypto Rebel). I am in blockchain since 2015, crypto 2017 and otherwise I have had a looooong career as a banker and also with Airbnb here in Amsterdam.\\n\\nI have been in love with NFTs since 2018 when I met Crypto Kitties guys for the first time in Hong Kong at some crypto conference. I have been doing some digital art and have a small collection on OpenSea and I also love crypto industry,it is really the best to work, earn, play and have lots of fun, we know how to make jokes about ourselves, dry humour and it all helps to survive the bear market and the ups and downs of BTC.\\n\\nIn my banking career I was a part of the innovation lab at ABN AMRO where we experimented with several products like real estate on blockchain, trade finance on blockchain etc. meaning that I have not had my first coin yet. it happened in 2016 before i left banking and went traveling to South America, and when i came back….boooom ICO explosion happened! And then I was totally mesmerised. I Wanted to be a part of it asap.\\n\\nAnd I joined ICORating to bring some order to the chaos lol.Then was SMC Capital, a year ago we launched Crypto Rebel — news and entertainment company and 3 months ago we started with LOCGame, which I founded.\\n\\n我是Mik Mironov，LegendsOfCrypto(LOCGame)和RBL实验室(隶属于Crypto Rebel)的创始人。我从2015年开始进入区块链并于2017年开始接触加密，除此之外的时间里我一直都是一名银行家，同时在位于阿姆斯特丹的Airbnb工作。从2018年开始我就爱上了NFT，当时我在香港的一个加密会议上第一次遇到了Crypto Kitties。\\n\\n之后我便一直在着手一些数字艺术，自己在OpenSea上也有一个小收藏品，可以说我非常喜欢加密领域，这真的是我心中最好的工作，不仅能获益也能得到很多乐趣。我们知道如何拿自己开玩笑，用些冷幽默，所有这些都有助于我们在熊市和BTC的起伏中幸存下来。\\n\\n在个人的银行从业生涯中，我是ABN AMRO创新实验室的一员，在那里我们试验了几种产品，比如区块链上的房地产、区块链上的贸易融资等，这意味着我还没有得到我的第一枚硬币。\\n\\n然而在2016年，当我离开银行业去南美旅行回来后，一切就这么发生了，Booom！ICO这的概念爆炸般的袭来！我完全被迷住了，就想尽快融入其中，随后我便加入了ICORing，试着为混乱的局面带来一些新秩序。 \\n\\n在这之后是SMC Capital，一年前我们成立了Crypto Rebel-一家新闻和娱乐公司，在创立公司的3个月前我们也开始了由我创立的LOCGame。\\n\\n主持人：橙子\\n\\n2\\\\.Explain what your project is:\\n给大家介绍一下你的项目吧\\n\\n嘉宾：Mik Mironov\\n\\nLegendsOfCrypto (LOCG) is a new Collectible NFT Card Game on the blockchain where players can battle it out to win valuable tokens and NFT items.\\n\\nLeveraging Decentralized Finance and DAO governance, LOCG creates a sustainable, community-driven gaming experience. The game itself is centered around the crypto industry pop culture, with playable characters like a Market Maker, Whale, including Binance’s very own CZ and other key proponents.\\n\\nThe game introduces a new style of play called Blockchain Control. Players place their cards upon the grid to control blocks, and whoever controls the most blocks when all blocks are controlled wins the match. It won’t be easy though, as each card has stats and abilities that can allow them to push their opponent’s cards off the grid and take-over their blocks. Win or lose, you still own your cards and those will inevitably go up in value due to the limited supply, rarity, and additions of new sets of cards that will bring players in from many different communities.We’re introducing an overarching platform that combines a strong community, creative NFT cards, and rewards mechanisms, all into one place.\\n\\nAt the core of the Legends of Crypto ecosystem is the platform's native LOCG utility token.\\n\\nLOCG is used for: \\n  \\n Fees for processing transactions and payments;\\n\\nl Rewards - staking, earn-to-play, kick-back when purchasing NFTs;\\n\\nl Used for governance votes to determine the future direction of the Game ecosystem development, charity donations (10% from NFT sales goes to charity), new categories of NFT items for issuance and more.\\n\\nLOCGame ecosystem includes:\\n\\nl Native marketplace connected to third-parties on MATIC and ETH.\\n\\nl Free-to-play, earn-to-play with reward in LOCG tokens.\\n\\nl Genesis edition fully dedicated to crypto industry famous characters.\\n\\nl Rare NFT items that can be used to collect, play, earn rewards and to have fun.\\n\\nLegendsOfCrypto(LOCG)是区块链上一款新的可收藏式NFT卡牌游戏，玩家可以在游戏中展开较量，赢得有价值的代币和NFT。利用去中心化金融和DAO治理，LOCG创造了一种可持续的并由社区驱动的游戏体验。游戏本身是围绕着加密领域的流行文化展开，游戏中的可玩角色包括做市商巨鲸，包括币安自己的CZ和其他关键支持者。\\n\\n该游戏引入了一种名为“区块控制”的新游戏风格。玩家将他们的卡放在网格上以控制区块，当所有区块都被控制时，谁控制的区块最多，谁就赢得比赛。但这并不容易，因为每张卡都有独特能力，可以让他们把对手的卡从网格上推开，接管他们的区块。无论输赢，你仍然拥有你的卡牌，由于供应有限、稀有性和新卡组的增加，这些卡牌的价值将不断地上升，这将使来自许多不同社区的玩家加入进来。我们正在将强大的社区、创造性的NFT卡片和奖励机制结合在一起。\\n\\nLegendsOfCrypto生态系统的核心是该平台的本地LOCG功能性代币。\\n\\nLOCG用于处理交易和付款的费用；\\n\\nl 奖励，质押、Play to earn、购买NFT的回扣；\\n\\nl 用于治理投票，以决定游戏生态系统未来的发展方向，慈善捐赠(10%的NFT销售额将用于慈善机构)，新的NFT发行类别等等。\\n\\nLOCGame生态系统包括：\\n\\nl 连接到MATIC和ETH上的第三方本地市场。\\n\\nl 免费游戏，游玩赚取和奖励LOCG代币。\\n\\nl 创世纪版本是完全致力于加密行业的著名人物。\\n\\n稀有的NFT物品可以用来收集、游玩、赚取奖励和获得娱乐。\\n\\n主持人：橙子\\n\\n3\\\\.How about the unique points and advantages of the project?\\n项目的独特点和优势是什么呢？\\n\\n嘉宾：Mik Mironov\\n\\nFirst off, all NFT cards provide proof of ownership via the blockchain, and solely belong to the user who purchased them — this means that your NFT is uniquely authentic and can be sold or traded only on your terms!\\nThe artwork for our NFTs is where we begin to truly shine, as we have some of the very best creative minds and artists coming up with the designs for our crypto influencer and meme characters. Each one has its own style and allure, giving users their own exclusive piece of a valuable collectible digital card.\\n\\nEvery card in our first Block Set, The Legends of Crypto, has various parameters that add to the gameplay, such as:\\n\\nl Influence\\n\\nl Innovation\\n\\nl Developer Skills\\n\\nl Net worth\\n\\nl Community\\n\\nl Impact\\n\\nCards will be sold by the pack, each pack will contain 5 cards initially at our Alpha Launch 2.0 in December this year. In December ONLY cards of lower in-game rarity will be sold in a VERY limited quantity. We will collect feedback from our community and players who got chosen for Early Access program.\\n\\nLater as we progress we will be offering our cards in different rarity as per this design (subject to change):\\n\\nEach set will have 60% Common cards, which drop more commonly but are still critical to deck building, 30% Uncommon cards, which are slightly more powerful, 15% Rare cards, which are quite powerful though obviously rare, and 5% Legendary cards, which can completely change a game when they’re drawn and played correctly.\\n\\nA deck will consist of 20 cards (15 initially at Alpha Launch 2.0) of the player’s choice, which must contain 10 commons, 6 uncommons, 3 rares, and 1 legendary. Games in LoCG will be relatively quick and brutal, and tournament games will require best of 3s in order to win.\\n\\nWe’ve done this in order to make the game more interactive and fun, where users can select and purchase which NFTs cards and card packs suit them the best.\\n\\n首先，所有NFT卡都将通过区块链提供所有权证明，并且只属于购买它们的用户--这意味着你的NFT是真实且唯一的，并且只能根据你的意愿进行销售或交易我们的NFT的艺术作品是我们开始真正发光的地方，因为我们有一些非常好的创意头脑和艺术家来为我们的加密货币影响者和备忘录人物设计。每个人都有自己独特的风格，给用户提供他们自己独家、宝贵的数字收藏品。\\n\\n在我们的第一个区块集，“Legends of Crypto”中，每张卡都有各种参数，增加了游戏性，例如：\\n\\\\*影响力\\n\\\\*创新能力\\n\\\\*开发者技能\\n\\\\*净值\\n\\\\*社区\\n\\n卡片将按以套为单位出售，在今年12月我们即将发布的Alpha2.0版上，每个套牌最初将包含5张卡片。12月份中只有游戏中稀有度较低的牌会做限量销售。我们将从我们的社区和被选中参加早期计划的玩家那里收集反馈。\\n\\n随着我们的进展，我们将根据此设计提供不同稀有度的卡片(视情况而定)：\\n每套卡组将有60%的普通卡，这些卡的掉落比较普遍，但对卡组的构建仍然至关重要；30%的中等卡，这些卡的威力稍大；15%的稀有卡，这些卡虽然明显稀有，且威力相当大；5%的传奇卡，这些卡一旦被抽中并正确使用，可以完全改变一场比赛。\\n一套卡组将由玩家选择的20张卡组成，其中必须包含10张普通卡、6���非普通卡、3张稀有卡和1张传奇卡。LoCG中的游戏将是相对快速和残酷的，锦标赛游戏将需要3局2胜制才能获胜。\\n\\n主持人：橙子\\n\\n4\\\\.Please tell us more about tokens and utilities?\\n请向大家介绍一下代币和使用场景\\n\\n嘉宾：Mik Mironov\\n\\nRegarding the tokens, with the help of blockchain and NFT technology finally game players become a part of the game economy. You can collect, play, earn and have fun at the same time! So for $LOCG you will be able to get a kick-back in LOCG when buying the NFT from our native marketplace (initial purchase)\\n\\nYou will be able to get it as a reward for playing the game (play to earn), stake LOCG to farm new NFT items, farm LOCG in liquidity pools and use it for payment within the ecosystem, get rewarded in earn-to-pay elements of the game, voting when we build the DAO and more. NFT holders will be able to stake them in a liquidity pool and get % from the prize pools as a reward in LOCG token. \\n\\nFor the value of $LOCG, we will have a governance mechanic by the end of this year, you will be able to vote on the issuance of new cards, new categories, game play, charity donation and more. There will be a LOC Council with minimum LOCG holding requirements to be able to propose those game changes, request new features, etc.So there is a lot of value and definitely will be a lot of rewards for investing in LOC Game Token.\\n\\n关于代币，在区块链和NFT技术的帮助下，游戏玩家终于成为游戏经济的一部分。你可以在收集、赚钱的同时获得乐趣! 因此，对于LOCG代币，当你从我们的市场购买NFT时，你将能够得到LOCG的回馈（初始购买）。\\n\\n你可以把它作为玩游戏的奖励（玩赚），质押LOCG来挖新的NFT，在流动性池中挖LOCG并用于生态系统中的支付，在游戏进行“玩赚”，在我们建立DAO时投票等等。NFT的持有者将可以把它们押在流动性池中，并从奖励池中获得LOCG代币作为奖励。\\n\\n对于LOCG的价值，我们将在今年年底上线治理机制，你将能够对新卡的发行、新类别、游戏玩法、慈善捐赠等进行投票。将会有一个最低LOCG持有量要求的LOC理事会，能够提出那些游戏变化，要求新的功能等。因此，投资LOC游戏代币有很多价值，同时肯定会有很多回报。\\n\\n主持人：橙子\\n\\n**5. Milestone achieved so far?**\\n\\n**目前取得了什么样的里程碑呢？**\\n\\n嘉宾：Mik Mironov\\n\\nFirst milestone of course is a succesful raise earlier this year and trust of all the investors who believe in us including our retail investor community, big funds like NGC, LD Capital, Signum and many other amazing guys\\n\\nOur first milestone was our SHO, strong holder offering, a type of the IDO that only DAOMaker has, was actually gonna be completed on April 28th. Of course, we are also really proud of having developed this project from scratch, and also managed to get a very strong, enviable list of investors including big names like Signum Capital, LD Capital, NGC, AU21, TerraVirtua and Block Dream Fund.\\n\\nPolygon is our official partner who also believes in our startup. We received a grant from Polygon and benefit from being a part of their ecosystem.\\n\\nAnother milestone is creating a new unique gameplay - we did not copy 125 times Hearthstone like the majority of the project. We went thru a more interesting way.\\n\\n30 November is our native marketplace launch where you can buy a VERY limited amount of NFTs，12 December - game launch in close Early Access program, applications are open here:  <https://www.locgame.io/sign-up>\\n\\nWe have received great and very encouraging  support from everyone. These investors will form an integral part of the LOC platform and will play key strategic roles to help us achieve our set out mission. We will continuously collaborate with them to help deliver on our promise to all users and the greater crypto community. In this regard, the investors have reiterated their commitment to the pursuit of common goals within the LOC roadmap through long-term relationships, which have many benefits for them. So a lot of success so far for the launch of the project.\\n\\n第一个里程碑当然是今年较早之前的成功募资，并得到了我们投资者们的信任，包括我们的散户投资者社区，NGC、LD Capital、Signum等大型基金和许多其他令人惊艳的伙伴们，我们的第一个里程碑是我们的SHO，这是一种只有DAOMaker才有的IDO，在4月28日完成。当然，我们也为从零开始开发这个项目感到非常自豪，也成功地获得了一个非常强大的、令人羡慕的投资者名单，包括Signum Capital、LD Capital、NGC、AU21、TerraVirtua和Block Dream Fund等大牌。\\n\\nPolygon是我们的官方合作伙伴，他也对我们的成立充满信心，因此我们也得到了Polygon的资助，并从成为他们生态系统的一部分中受益。\\n\\n另一个里程碑是创造了一个独特的新游戏-我们没有像大多数项目那样复制125次Hearthstone。我们走了一条更有趣的路。\\n\\n11月30日是我们的本地市场发布，在这里您可以购买数量极其有限的NFT。此外，游戏会于12月12日在Close Early Access program中发布，以下是访问链接：<https://www.locgame.io/sign-up>\\n\\n我们已经从每个人那里得到了巨大的、非常令人鼓舞的支持。这些投资者将成为LOC平台不可或缺的一部分，并将发挥关键的战略作用，帮助我们实现既定的使命。我们将继续与他们合作，以帮助实现我们对所有用户和广大加密货币社区的承诺。在这方面，投资者重申了他们的承诺，即通过长期的合作关系，追求LOC路线图内的共同目标，这对他们来说有很多好处。因此，到目前为止，项目的启动取得了很大的成功。\\n\\n主持人：橙子\\n\\n6\\\\.Road map and plans for the future?\\n有路径发展规划和未来的规划能分享一下吗？\\n\\n嘉宾：Mik Mironov\\n\\nThe easiest way to check our RoadMap is to look up on our website: <https://www.locgame.io/roadmap>\\n\\nRight now we are close to launching our NFT Marketplace and will have an exclusive sale of our Genesis Edition cards. The first NFT sale will be opened community early supporters and early investors only, so stay tuned.\\n\\nand then will come the Alpha 2.0 Game launch on 12 December, you will be able to play the game ONLY if you have the 15 cards deck of course :) and selected during our application process.\\n\\nBeta versions and full-fledged versions with all DeFI and DAO elements we envision are planned for Q1-3 2022.\\n\\nOur plan for LOCGame also includes expanding the cards categories. We started with crypto characters in this Genesis Edition. And then, we'll be able to expand into crypto cities, decks based on partnerships and many more.Imagination is the limit!\\n\\nEventually, on a broader, long-term plan, RBL Labs aims to build more cool games on blockchain with a heavy focus on NFT, not necessarily card-based games. We are slowly learning in this journey but this is a great start and we are excited for the future.\\n\\nJust want to add that even before all of that, people can already get involved in our exclusive Discord and all other channels and social media, we have had so much fun there with a vibrant and active community and contests, competitions and more!\\n\\n最简单了解路线图的方式就是从我们的官网: <https://www.locgame.io/roadmap>\\n\\n现在，我们即将推出我们的NFT市场，并将独家销售我们的创世版卡片。第一次NFT销售将只对早期支持者和早期投资者开放，所以请继续关注，也就是上面提到的11月30日。\\n\\n然后将于12月12日发布Alpha2.0版的游戏，只有当您拥有15张纸牌并在申请过程中被我们选中时，您才能参与游玩。\\n\\n我们计划在2022年第一季度至第三季度推出测试版和包含我们设想的所有包含Defi和DAO元素的完整版本。\\n\\n现在，我们对LOC游戏的计划还包括扩大卡片类别。在这个创世版中，我们从加密货币角色开始。然后，我们将能够扩展到加密城市，基于合作伙伴关系的卡组以及更多。想象空间是无限的。\\n\\n最终，在一个更长期计划中，RBL实验室的目标是在区块链上建立更多很酷的游戏，重点是NFT，不一定是基于卡片的游戏。我们在这个旅程中慢慢学习，但这是一个很好的开始，我们对未来充满期待。\\n\\n我想补充的是，即使在这之前，人们已经可以参与到我们的独家Discord和所有其他渠道和社交媒体中，我们在那里有很多乐趣，有一个充满活力和活跃的社区和竞赛，比赛和更多的东西!\\n\\n主持人：橙子\\n\\n今天的问题到此结束，下面大家如果有问题，可以自由提问\\\\~\\nThat's the end of today's question. If you have any questions, feel free to ask questions.\\n\\nA16Z：\\n\\nThanks Mik. I wanna know how you guys plan to promote and market your program,\\n\\nto let more people know this great program.\\n\\n谢谢Mik，我想知道你们如何推广和运营，让更多人知道这个伟大的项目。\\n\\n嘉宾：Mik Mironov\\n\\nThat's a good question. Before we launch any big promos we do want to make sure that our community, which is quite big likes the gameplay that we build. And our step n1 is to engage with our community more to get feedback. Besides our main global telegram/discord and twitter group we have amazing active communities in China, Korea, Vietnam, Turkey, Indonesia - so we wil be even closer to our core communities there.\\n\\nAfter we make sure that our product is great, we will engage in larger marketing campaigns with the influencers and media. We already have amazing support from guys like Bitboy, Crypto Banter and so on, they will have their own cards within the game : check out this one for example <https://www.locgame.io/heroes/bitboy>\\n\\n这个问题问得挺好。在我们推出任何大型宣传活动之前，我们希望确保这个相当大的社区喜欢我们建立的游戏性。我们的第一步是更多地参与社区，以获得反馈。除了我们主要的全球电报/Discord和推特之外，我们在中国、韩国、越南、土耳其和印度尼西亚都有相当活跃的社区-因此我们将更接近我们在该地的核心社区。\\n\\n在我们确定产品足够优秀后，我们将与有影响力的人和媒体一起进行更大规模的营销活动。目前我们已经得到了BitBoy、Crypto Challter等游戏玩家的大力支持，他们也将在游戏中拥有自己的卡片：例如这张：<https://www.locgame.io/heroes/bitboy>\",\"timestamp\":1637725869,\"title\":\"Locgame-Polygon生态的卡牌GameFi~\"},\"digest\":\"dmu-EBHZb24RPNrtlD7MXqIZStixb63fGMsM2zekboo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8c902B8839010BB1761201d42f788e7eD9FCFD77\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gYEHeLobyynEioc4NlUkGKqnxzFfB3t5i6QkwT_CNnY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"z9ACjb3YB8DsqudWtl7-aPO0SrE053zis5YIyfp9StU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"BTBNLwpFyF3CNKT6GClxKxITUZ7fNTNirrtFXdKyVXjGgQfOh8_Qtnt0tT9uYT8Nr0B6JRVblFaYS2259saQLA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc259978b0f7578186e155bcc6d84777a68303ff51bd8af4bd53e9f1fb39eb4e46736834fb96bb5fcf14986a46fc3e91d63a3e9e3cefe248da9fde4f4e20b653c1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gYEHeLobyynEioc4NlUkGKqnxzFfB3t5i6QkwT_CNnY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"z9ACjb3YB8DsqudWtl7-aPO0SrE053zis5YIyfp9StU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"dmu-EBHZb24RPNrtlD7MXqIZStixb63fGMsM2zekboo\"}"